    <title>动态规划（Dynamic Programming）</title>
    <link href="/2026/06/12/Dynamic-Programming/"/>
    <url>/2026/06/12/Dynamic-Programming/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="一、定义与原理"><a href="#一、定义与原理" class="headerlink" title="一、定义与原理"></a>一、定义与原理</h3><p>动态规划（DP）是一种通过<strong>把原问题分解为相对简单的子问题</strong>，并<strong>保存子问题的解</strong>来避免重复计算，从而高效求解最优化问题的方法。其核心思想是：</p><ul><li><strong>最优子结构</strong>：一个问题的最优解包含其子问题的最优解。</li><li><strong>重叠子问题</strong>：递归求解时，子问题被重复计算多次，DP 通过记忆化（memoization）或自底向上填表来消除重复。</li></ul><p>通常有两种实现方式：</p><ul><li><strong>自顶向下（记忆化搜索）</strong>：从原问题出发递归求解，每计算一个子问题就存储结果。</li><li><strong>自底向上（表格迭代）</strong>：从最小子问题开始，按顺序逐步推出更大问题的解。</li></ul><p><strong>简单例子</strong>：斐波那契数列。<code>F(n) = F(n-1) + F(n-2)</code>，直接递归有大量重复计算；用 DP 数组保存已算出的值，时间复杂度从 O(2^n) 降至 O(n)。</p><hr><h3 id="二、适用场景（典型问题）"><a href="#二、适用场景（典型问题）" class="headerlink" title="二、适用场景（典型问题）"></a>二、适用场景（典型问题）</h3><ol><li><strong>最值问题</strong>：如最长递增子序列、最小路径和、最大子数组和。</li><li><strong>计数问题</strong>：如爬楼梯（多少种方式）、不同路径、整数拆分。</li><li><strong>可行性问题</strong>：如能否分割等和子集、是否能到达终点。</li><li><strong>字符串匹配&#x2F;编辑距离</strong>：如最长公共子序列、编辑距离、通配符匹配。</li></ol><p>关键词：最优、最值、方案数、是否可行、子序列、子数组、背包、区间 DP、状态机。</p><hr><h3 id="三、不能用的场景"><a href="#三、不能用的场景" class="headerlink" title="三、不能用的场景"></a>三、不能用的场景</h3><ul><li><strong>无最优子结构</strong>：问题的最优解不依赖于子问题的最优解，例如求有向图中的最长简单路径（子路径最优不一定能拼成全局最优）。</li><li><strong>无重叠子问题</strong>：分治法每次产生全新子问题（如快速排序），DP 没有收益。</li><li><strong>状态空间过大</strong>：状态维度爆炸（如三维以上且边界很大），时间和空间不可接受，需考虑其他算法（贪心、启发式）。</li><li><strong>存在后效性</strong>：某阶段的状态会影响后续决策的约束条件，且无法通过增加状态维度消除（例如某些路径问题需要记录访问历史）。</li></ul><hr><h3 id="四、简单代码示例（Java）"><a href="#四、简单代码示例（Java）" class="headerlink" title="四、简单代码示例（Java）"></a>四、简单代码示例（Java）</h3><p><strong>问题</strong>：爬楼梯（LeetCode 70），每次可爬 1 或 2 阶，求爬到 n 阶的不同方法数。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">ClimbStairs</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">climbStairs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[n + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>        dp[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 1阶:1种</span><br>        dp[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;  <span class="hljs-comment">// 2阶:2种</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;<br>            dp[i] = dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] + dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">2</span>];<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dp[n];<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 空间优化：只用两个变量</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">climbStairsOpt</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> n;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">a</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, b = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">c</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> a + b;<br>            a = b;<br>            b = c;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> b;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h3 id="五、📚-例题精讲与分析"><a href="#五、📚-例题精讲与分析" class="headerlink" title="五、📚 例题精讲与分析"></a>五、📚 例题精讲与分析</h3><h4 id="📖-1-70-爬楼梯：斐波那契型-DP"><a href="#📖-1-70-爬楼梯：斐波那契型-DP" class="headerlink" title="📖 1. 70. 爬楼梯：斐波那契型 DP"></a>📖 1. 70. 爬楼梯：斐波那契型 DP</h4><p><strong>题目描述</strong>：假设你正在爬楼梯，需要 n 阶才能到达楼顶。每次可以爬 1 或 2 个台阶，有多少种不同的方法？</p><p><strong>核心转化</strong>：到达第 i 阶的方法数 &#x3D; 到达 i-1 阶的方法数 + 到达 i-2 阶的方法数（因为最后一步跨 1 阶或 2 阶）。</p><p><strong>算法步骤</strong>：</p><ol><li>定义 <code>dp[i]</code> 为到达第 i 阶的方法数。</li><li>初始化 <code>dp[1]=1</code>，<code>dp[2]=2</code>。</li><li>从 <code>i=3</code> 到 <code>n</code>，执行 <code>dp[i] = dp[i-1] + dp[i-2]</code>。</li><li>返回 <code>dp[n]</code>。</li></ol><p><strong>Java 代码</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">climbStairs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (n == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[n+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>    dp[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    dp[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span>; i &lt;= n; i++) &#123;<br>        dp[i] = dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] + dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">2</span>];<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dp[n];<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>复杂度分析</strong>：时间 O(n)，空间 O(n)；可优化至 O(1)。</p><p><strong>易错点 &#x2F; 小技巧</strong>：n&#x3D;0 时题意通常不出现；注意边界 <code>n=1</code> 直接返回。</p><hr><h4 id="📖-2-53-最大子数组和：经典-Kadane-算法"><a href="#📖-2-53-最大子数组和：经典-Kadane-算法" class="headerlink" title="📖 2. 53. 最大子数组和：经典 Kadane 算法"></a>📖 2. 53. 最大子数组和：经典 Kadane 算法</h4><p><strong>题目描述</strong>：给定整数数组 nums，找出一个具有最大和的连续子数组（子数组最少包含一个元素），返回其最大和。</p><p><strong>核心转化</strong>：<code>dp[i]</code> 表示以 <code>nums[i]</code> 结尾的最大子数组和。状态转移：<code>dp[i] = max(nums[i], dp[i-1] + nums[i])</code>。最终答案是 <code>max(dp[0..n-1])</code>。</p><p><strong>算法步骤</strong>：</p><ol><li>初始化 <code>dp[0] = nums[0]</code>，<code>maxSum = nums[0]</code>。</li><li>遍历 i 从 1 到 n-1：<ul><li><code>dp[i] = Math.max(nums[i], dp[i-1] + nums[i])</code></li><li>更新 <code>maxSum = Math.max(maxSum, dp[i])</code></li></ul></li><li>返回 <code>maxSum</code>。</li></ol><p><strong>Java 代码</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">maxSubArray</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">n</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[n];<br>    dp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = nums[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">maxSum</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> dp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;<br>        dp[i] = Math.max(nums[i], dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] + nums[i]);<br>        maxSum = Math.max(maxSum, dp[i]);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> maxSum;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">// 空间优化</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">maxSubArrayOpt</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">pre</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>], maxSum = pre;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt; nums.length; i++) &#123;<br>        pre = Math.max(nums[i], pre + nums[i]);<br>        maxSum = Math.max(maxSum, pre);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> maxSum;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>复杂度分析</strong>：时间 O(n)，空间 O(1)。</p><p><strong>易错点 &#x2F; 小技巧</strong>：不能直接取 <code>max(dp[i-1]+nums[i], dp[i-1])</code>，因为子数组必须连续；如果全为负数，答案是最大负数而非 0。</p><hr><h4 id="📖-3-300-最长递增子序列：O-n²-与-O-n-log-n"><a href="#📖-3-300-最长递增子序列：O-n²-与-O-n-log-n" class="headerlink" title="📖 3. 300. 最长递增子序列：O(n²) 与 O(n log n)"></a>📖 3. 300. 最长递增子序列：O(n²) 与 O(n log n)</h4><p><strong>题目描述</strong>：给你一个整数数组 nums，找到其中最长严格递增子序列的长度（子序列不要求连续）。</p><p><strong>核心转化</strong>：定义 <code>dp[i]</code> 为以 <code>nums[i]</code> 结尾的最长递增子序列长度。转移：<code>dp[i] = max(dp[j]) + 1</code>，其中 <code>j &lt; i</code> 且 <code>nums[j] &lt; nums[i]</code>。最终答案为 <code>max(dp)</code>。</p><p><strong>算法步骤</strong>（O(n²)）：</p><ol><li>初始化 <code>dp</code> 全为 1。</li><li>双重循环：外层 i，内层 j (0..i-1)，若 <code>nums[j] &lt; nums[i]</code> 则 <code>dp[i] = max(dp[i], dp[j]+1)</code>。</li><li>返回 <code>max(dp)</code>。</li></ol><p><strong>Java 代码（O(n²)）</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">lengthOfLIS</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] nums)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">n</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> nums.length;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[n];<br>    Arrays.fill(dp, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">maxLen</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">j</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; j &lt; i; j++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (nums[j] &lt; nums[i]) &#123;<br>                dp[i] = Math.max(dp[i], dp[j] + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        maxLen = Math.max(maxLen, dp[i]);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> maxLen;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>复杂度分析</strong>：时间 O(n²)，空间 O(n)。可用二分查找优化至 O(n log n)。</p><p><strong>易错点 &#x2F; 小技巧</strong>：子序列不要求连续，所以内层循环 j 从 0 到 i-1 全检查；O(n log n) 方案中维护一个 tails 数组，表示长度为 k 的递增子序列的最小末尾值。</p><hr><h4 id="📖-4-1143-最长公共子序列：二维-DP"><a href="#📖-4-1143-最长公共子序列：二维-DP" class="headerlink" title="📖 4. 1143. 最长公共子序列：二维 DP"></a>📖 4. 1143. 最长公共子序列：二维 DP</h4><p><strong>题目描述</strong>：给定两个字符串 text1 和 text2，返回它们的最长公共子序列的长度（子序列不要求连续）。</p><p><strong>核心转化</strong>：定义 <code>dp[i][j]</code> 表示 text1[0..i-1] 和 text2[0..j-1] 的 LCS 长度。转移：</p><ul><li>若 <code>text1[i-1] == text2[j-1]</code>，则 <code>dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1] + 1</code></li><li>否则 <code>dp[i][j] = max(dp[i-1][j], dp[i][j-1])</code></li></ul><p><strong>算法步骤</strong>：</p><ol><li>创建 <code>(m+1)*(n+1)</code> 的 dp 数组，初始化为 0。</li><li>双重循环 i&#x3D;1..m，j&#x3D;1..n，按转移公式填表。</li><li>返回 <code>dp[m][n]</code>。</li></ol><p><strong>Java 代码</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">longestCommonSubsequence</span><span class="hljs-params">(String text1, String text2)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">m</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> text1.length(), n = text2.length();<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[][] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[m+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][n+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= m; i++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">j</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; j &lt;= n; j++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (text1.charAt(i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>) == text2.charAt(j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)) &#123;<br>                dp[i][j] = dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                dp[i][j] = Math.max(dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][j], dp[i][j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]);<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dp[m][n];<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>复杂度分析</strong>：时间 O(m×n)，空间 O(m×n)，可优化至 O(min(m,n))。</p><p><strong>易错点 &#x2F; 小技巧</strong>：dp 数组多开一行一列避免了边界判断；字符相等时必须从 <code>[i-1][j-1]</code> 转移，不能从上边或左边，否则会重复计数。</p><hr><h4 id="📖-5-322-零钱兑换：完全背包问题"><a href="#📖-5-322-零钱兑换：完全背包问题" class="headerlink" title="📖 5. 322. 零钱兑换：完全背包问题"></a>📖 5. 322. 零钱兑换：完全背包问题</h4><p><strong>题目描述</strong>：给定不同面额的硬币 coins 和一个总金额 amount，计算可以凑成总金额所需的最少硬币个数。如果无法凑成，返回 -1。每种硬币数量无限。</p><p><strong>核心转化</strong>：完全背包（每种物品无限取），求恰好装满背包的最小价值（硬币个数）。定义 <code>dp[i]</code> 为凑成金额 i 所需的最少硬币数。初始化 <code>dp[0]=0</code>，其余为 <code>amount+1</code>（不可达标记）。转移：<code>dp[i] = min(dp[i], dp[i - coin] + 1)</code>。</p><p><strong>算法步骤</strong>：</p><ol><li>创建 <code>dp</code> 数组长度 <code>amount+1</code>，填充大值 <code>amount+1</code>。</li><li><code>dp[0] = 0</code>。</li><li>外层遍历金额 i 从 1 到 amount，内层遍历每种硬币 coin，若 <code>i &gt;= coin</code>，更新 <code>dp[i] = Math.min(dp[i], dp[i-coin] + 1)</code>。</li><li>若 <code>dp[amount] == amount+1</code> 返回 -1，否则返回 <code>dp[amount]</code>。</li></ol><p><strong>Java 代码</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">coinChange</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] coins, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> amount)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[amount + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>    Arrays.fill(dp, amount + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>    dp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= amount; i++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> coin : coins) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (i &gt;= coin &amp;&amp; dp[i - coin] != amount + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>                dp[i] = Math.min(dp[i], dp[i - coin] + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dp[amount] == amount + <span class="hljs-number">1</span> ? -<span class="hljs-number">1</span> : dp[amount];<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>复杂度分析</strong>：时间 O(amount × n)，空间 O(amount)，n 为硬币种类数。</p><p><strong>易错点 &#x2F; 小技巧</strong>：初始化不能用 Integer.MAX_VALUE，否则加 1 会溢出；外层遍历金额，内层遍历硬币（完全背包常见顺序）；如果先硬币后金额且用正序遍历，也是完全背包，结果相同。</p><hr><h4 id="📖-6-72-编辑距离：困难题，二维-DP"><a href="#📖-6-72-编辑距离：困难题，二维-DP" class="headerlink" title="📖 6. 72. 编辑距离：困难题，二维 DP"></a>📖 6. 72. 编辑距离：困难题，二维 DP</h4><p><strong>题目描述</strong>：给你两个单词 word1 和 word2，请返回将 word1 转换成 word2 所使用的最少操作数。你可以对一个单词进行如下三种操作：插入一个字符、删除一个字符、替换一个字符。</p><p><strong>核心转化</strong>：定义 <code>dp[i][j]</code> 表示 word1 的前 i 个字符转换成 word2 的前 j 个字符所需的最少操作数。转移：</p><ul><li>若 <code>word1[i-1] == word2[j-1]</code>，则 <code>dp[i][j] = dp[i-1][j-1]</code>（无需操作）</li><li>否则 <code>dp[i][j] = 1 + min(删除：dp[i-1][j], 插入：dp[i][j-1], 替换：dp[i-1][j-1])</code></li></ul><p><strong>算法步骤</strong>：</p><ol><li>初始化边界：<code>dp[i][0] = i</code>（全部删除），<code>dp[0][j] = j</code>（全部插入）。</li><li>双重循环 i&#x3D;1..m，j&#x3D;1..n，按转移公式填表。</li><li>返回 <code>dp[m][n]</code>。</li></ol><p><strong>Java 代码</strong>：</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs java"><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">minDistance</span><span class="hljs-params">(String word1, String word2)</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">m</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> word1.length(), n = word2.length();<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span>[][] dp = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">int</span>[m+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][n+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt;= m; i++) dp[i][<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = i;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">j</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; j &lt;= n; j++) dp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>][j] = j;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">i</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= m; i++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-variable">j</span> <span class="hljs-operator">=</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; j &lt;= n; j++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (word1.charAt(i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>) == word2.charAt(j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)) &#123;<br>                dp[i][j] = dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>            &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>                dp[i][j] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + Math.min(dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][j], <br>                               Math.min(dp[i][j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>], dp[i-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][j-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]));<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dp[m][n];<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>复杂度分析</strong>：时间 O(m×n)，空间 O(m×n)，可优化至 O(min(m,n))。</p><p><strong>易错点 &#x2F; 小技巧</strong>：注意三种操作的对应关系：删除对应 <code>dp[i-1][j]</code>，插入对应 <code>dp[i][j-1]</code>，替换对应 <code>dp[i-1][j-1]</code>；初始化边界容易遗漏。</p><hr><p>最后汇总所有题目，其中题号是 LeetCode 的超链接：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">题号 (ID)</th><th align="left">题目名称</th><th align="left">核心考点</th><th align="left">题目难度</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left"><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/climbing-stairs/"><strong>70</strong></a></td><td align="left">爬楼梯</td><td align="left">斐波那契型 DP，一维状态转移</td><td align="left">🟢 简单</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-subarray/"><strong>53</strong></a></td><td align="left">最大子数组和</td><td align="left">Kadane 算法，以 i 结尾的子数组最值</td><td align="left">🟢 简单</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/longest-increasing-subsequence/"><strong>300</strong></a></td><td align="left">最长递增子序列</td><td align="left">LIS，O(n²) 或 O(n log n) 二分</td><td align="left">🟡 中等</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/longest-common-subsequence/"><strong>1143</strong></a></td><td align="left">最长公共子序列</td><td align="left">二维 DP，字符串双序列匹配</td><td align="left">🟡 中等</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/coin-change/"><strong>322</strong></a></td><td align="left">零钱兑换</td><td align="left">完全背包，凑金额的最小硬币数</td><td align="left">🟡 中等</td></tr><tr><td align="left"><a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/edit-distance/"><strong>72</strong></a></td><td align="left">编辑距离</td><td align="left">二维 DP，三种操作的最少代价</td><td align="left">🔴 困难</td></tr></tbody></table><pre><code class="hljs"></code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
    
